OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy and
OL,6,Fmainly dry with the odd light shower.
OL,7,FThis afternoon will be dry with some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells breaking
OL,9,Fthrough.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,12,Fsome late brightness. Rain will spread
OL,13,Feast across all parts during the early
OL,14,Fhours, becoming dry across the Isles
OL,15,Flater.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FOutbreaks of rain will clear
OL,18,Faway east through the morning. Then
OL,19,Fthe rest of the day will bright spells
OL,20,Fand scattered showers. Colder than of
OL,21,Flate.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
