OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FDry and
OL,6,Fbright for most of Friday but rain
OL,7,Fspreading northeast in the evening and
OL,8,Fovernight. Bright spells and showers
OL,9,Fover the weekend, showers more
OL,10,Ffrequent on Sunday.
